{"ProductId":"12","Title":"Gallery<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Steel","ShortDescription":"Grooved panel steel carriage house garage doors","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/gallery-steel-ug-long-rec14-595.webp?sfvrsn=a7ceae04_9","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/gallerysteel","Overview":"<h3>Style Meets Strength</h3><h4>Built Your Way</h4><p>Choose from 3-, 2-, or 1-layer construction to fit your needs and budget. Each option is crafted from tough steel for daily reliability.</p><h4>Custom Looks</h4><p>Pick short or long grooved panels, add windows and decorative hardware, and select from 16 standard colors including rich <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/ultra-grain\">Ultra-Grain&reg; wood-look</a> and modern Lustra&trade; matte finishes. Or try over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; custom shades</a> to get exactly the right color.</p><h4>Comfortable &amp; Quiet</h4><p>Insulation options include <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane</a> or classic polystyrene, providing R-values from 6.5 up to 18.4. That means a more comfortable garage, year-round.</p><h4>Weather Ready</h4><p>Optional <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> adds security in high-wind areas, so your door is as tough as it is stylish.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>How It&rsquo;s Made: Gallery&reg; Steel</h3><p>The Gallery&reg; Steel door is built to handle whatever your day throws at it. Each door is crafted with sturdy steel inside and out, sandwiching a layer of high-performance <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane</a> or standard polystyrene insulation. This multi-layer construction helps keep your garage warmer in winter, cooler in summer, and quieter all year long.</p><p>Clopay&rsquo;s rust-prevention system protects your investment with hot-dipped galvanizing, a tough metal oxide pretreatment, and a baked-on finish for lasting beauty with minimal upkeep. A replaceable vinyl bottom weather seal in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer helps block out drafts and water, while heavy-duty hardware and 10-ball nylon rollers keep everything running smoothly.</p><p>Safety comes standard, thanks to the patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg;, and removable window grilles make cleaning a breeze. Altogether, you get a door that&rsquo;s durable, low-maintenance, and designed to look great for years.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-gallery-steel.webp?sfvrsn=f0d415d7_4\" alt=\"Gallery Steel\" sf-size=\"6672\" /><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Steel</li><li>Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane or Polystyrene Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Gallery Steel","DisplayIndex":8,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/gallery-steel","ColorDisclaimer":"<p><strong><em></em></strong>The Gallery&reg; Steel door comes in a near endless variety of colors and finishes. Choose from standard colors like White, Almond, Desert Tan, Sandtone, Chocolate, Bronze, Mocha Brown, and Charcoal for an ageless look that fits any exterior.</p><p>For something extra special, explore premium colors. Get the warmth of real wood with Ultra-Grain&reg; Oak finishes in Medium, Dark, Walnut, or Slate, each with your choice of subtle stucco or authentic woodgrain textures. For a modern twist, try Lustra&trade; matte colors in Charcoal, Black, or Silver, or the bold Iron Ore finish.</p><p>If you need a one-of-a-kind shade, the Color Blast&reg; program lets you pick from over 1,500 custom colors. Just remember, some colors are exclusive to certain door constructions and textures, and premium options are available on 24-gauge steel.</p><p>(S) Stucco Texture<br />(W) Woodgrain Texture<br />(M) Matte Texture</p><p><em>*Not available on Gallery Steel 1- and 2-Layer doors<br />&plusmn;Only available on Gallery Steel 1- and 2-layer doors<br />Premium Colors are subject to additional fee and only available on 24-gauge steel.<br />Custom color available through <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> program.<br />**Promotion valid on new door purchases in the Iron Ore color; savings vary by door size and location.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>When it&rsquo;s time to select the windows and top section for your Gallery&reg; Steel door, keep a few things in mind. If you&rsquo;re going for a time-honored look, choose a solid top section. If you want to let in more light or add a unique architectural detail, check out the window options. They range from traditional rectangular panes to arched styles and decorative grilles.</p><p>There are designs to suit every taste: plain glass for a simple look, grilles for a hint of tradition, or even wrought iron-inspired acrylic windows for a bit of fancy. Double doors get exclusive double-arch window styles for standout curb appeal.</p><p><em>*Acrylic window designs.<br />Note for Double Top Sections: These are specific to double car doors, in addition to options above.</em></p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>The handles and hardware on any garage door help create the final look, whether that’s a hint of traditional carriage house charm or a custom accent. Every Gallery® Steel door comes standard with classic spade lift handles, but you can tailor the finishing touches. Choose from a range of optional handle styles including spear, colonial, or the distinctive twisted “T” and “L” handles. Add matching escutcheon plates for a polished, refined look.</p>\r\n<p>Complement your handle choice with coordinating step plates and decorative strap hinges, available in spade, spear, or colonial designs. All hardware is built from sturdy materials and finished in black.</p>\r\n","DesignDisclaimer":"<p>Depending on door height, exact door appearance and number of sections may be different than illustrations above. <a href=\"http://clopaypdfs.com/pdf_files/RSDR-RESISTACKGUIDE-20.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" data-sf-ec-immutable=\"\">Click here</a> for complete details.</p><p>18\" sections not available on 1- and 2-layer doors.</p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (5-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr5l-des11-rec13-tampa-showcase.webp?sfvrsn=d9bffbb6_1","Id":"30","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyonridge","DisplayIndex":3,"ShortDescription":"Insulated carriage house garage doors with faux wood composite cladding and overlays","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (5-Layer)"},{"Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Carriage House (4-Layer)","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/cr4l-d21-rec13-afp143r.webp?sfvrsn=8ae1d536_3","Id":"29","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-4-layer","DisplayIndex":4,"ShortDescription":"Stylish, low maintenance and insulated faux wood garage doors","AlternativeText":"Canyon Ridge Carriage House (4-Layer)"},{"Title":"Coachman<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup>","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/coachman-d21-rec13-davidson-595.webp?sfvrsn=d3817fcc_10","Id":"11","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/coachman","DisplayIndex":12,"ShortDescription":"The perfect blend of beauty and practicality, these doors are crafted of durable steel and insulation topped with a textured composite overlay","AlternativeText":"Coachman"},{"Title":"Grand Harbor<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup>","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/grand-harbor-schanen-595.webp?sfvrsn=91e18ec0_2","Id":"27","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/grandharbor","DisplayIndex":13,"ShortDescription":"When budget is the deciding factor, this low-maintenance, insulation-optional steel frame carriage house style garage door combines clean lines and classic charm","AlternativeText":"Grand Harbor"},{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Custom","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-le-chevron-595.webp?sfvrsn=2b65fc56_8","Id":"8","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve-custom","DisplayIndex":15,"ShortDescription":"Both stunning and substantial, every Reserve® Wood garage door embodies our total commitment to design, detail and craftsmanship","AlternativeText":"Reserve Wood Custom"},{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Limited Edition","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-limimted-edition-design5-arch1-meranti-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=d5180ef3_10","Id":"10","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve","DisplayIndex":16,"ShortDescription":"Exceptional beauty, durability and energy efficiency","AlternativeText":"Reserve Wood Limited Edition"},{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Semi-Custom","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-semi-custom-design4-rec14-window-hemlock-garage-door-822.webp?sfvrsn